sentences.english: Their goal is to serve me a relevant ad everywhere I am.
sentences.chinese: 他们的目标是无处不在的为我提供相关的广告。

sentences.english: That's how schoolyard bullies run playgrounds and global godfathers do it everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 这就是校园欺负运行操场和全球教父做到无处不在。

sentences.english: Everything from prothetic limbs to pre-fabricated houses will be made using similar printing technology.
sentences.chinese: 从医用假肢到预制房屋，3D打印技术可谓无处不在。

sentences.english: The music is all around us, all you have to do, is listening.
sentences.chinese: 只要倾耳聆听，音乐便无处不在。

sentences.english: The role is really supposed to be omnipotent and omnipresent.
sentences.chinese: 这个角色无处不在，无所不能。

sentences.english: SECOND NAZARENE: He is in every place my lord but it is hard to find Him.
sentences.chinese: 陛下，这个人无处不在，要找到他，太难了。

sentences.english: These guys are everywhere and nowhere.
sentences.chinese: 这些人无处不在，却又无影无形。

sentences.english: Glorious refuge of sentient being, everywhere in the universe.
sentences.chinese: 有情众生的怙主，大千世界你无处不在。

sentences.english: Your kingdom is glorious and your generosity everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 你的天国辉煌灿烂，你的慷慨无处不在。

sentences.english: The bath happiness without fear, the heart also will be everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 幸福无惧，心灵的沐浴也将无处不在。

sentences.english: Parents cannot possibly control television, with its titanic omnipresence.
sentences.chinese: 父母不能控制电视，因为电视实在是无处不在。

sentences.english: The etiquettes of the Tibetan people are omnipresent and diversified.
sentences.chinese: 礼仪在藏民族生活中无时无处不在，其形式多种多样。

sentences.english: God couldn't be anywhere, that's why he made aunties.
sentences.chinese: 上帝不可能无处不在，所以他创造了女人。

sentences.english: Protein phosphorylation has emerged as a ubiquitous regulatory switch in cell signaling networks.
sentences.chinese: 蛋白磷酸化在控制细胞信号传导中无处不在。

sentences.english: Crazy amount of C. C. T. V. cameras, uniformed officers everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 疯狂的监控摄像头和穿制服的人无处不在。

sentences.english: But the competition is catching up. Bing sucks.
